The task will use a scoring system to evaluate the accuracy of the prediction. The scoring criteria are as follows:
- Setosa: 1 point for sepal length, 1 point for sepal width, 1 point for petal length, 1 point for petal width
- Versicolor: 1 point for sepal length, 1 point for sepal width, 0.5 points for petal length, 0.5 points for petal width
- Virginica: 0.5 points for sepal length, 0.5 points for sepal width, 1 point for petal length, 1 point for petal width

## Feedback
The task will provide feedback on the accuracy of the prediction, indicating whether the prediction is correct or not, and providing a score based on the scoring criteria.

## Assumptions
The task assumes that the input dimensions are in centimeters (cm) and that the dataset is up-to-date and accurate.
