  - Average petal length: 6-9 cm
  - Average petal width: 2-4 cm
  - Average sepal length: 6-8 cm
  - Average sepal width: 2.5-4 cm

## Comparison Criteria
The input dimensions will be compared to the average dimensions of each species to predict the species of the iris. The criteria for comparison are as follows:
- Setosa:
  - Petal length < 3 cm
  - Petal width < 1.5 cm
  - Sepal length < 5.5 cm
  - Sepal width < 3.5 cm
- Versicolor:
  - Petal length < 5 cm
  - Petal width < 2 cm
